+---------------------------+
            ^
            | 1
            | 
            | *
+---------------------------+
|     MonitoringRecord      |
+---------------------------+
| - timestamp               |
| - rawData                 |
| - processedData           |
| - contextSnapshot         |
+---------------------------+
| + enrich()                |
| + classify()              |
+---------------------------+


+---------------------------+
|  VirtualSoftwareAgent     |
+---------------------------+
| - vsaId                   |
| - name                    |
| - status                  |
| - knowledgeBase           |
+---------------------------+
| + analyze()               |
| + detectAnomaly()         |
| + generateReport()        |
+---------------------------+
            ^
            | 1
            | 
            | *
+---------------------------+
|     AnalysisResult        |
+---------------------------+
| - anomalyDetected         |
| - severityScore           |
| - severityLevel           |
| - reasoning               |
+---------------------------+
| + summarize()             |
+---------------------------+


+---------------------------+
|  DecisionActionEngine     |
+---------------------------+
| - rules                   |
| - severityModel           |
+---------------------------+
| + evaluate()              |
| + recommendActions()      |
| + escalateIfNeeded()      |
+---------------------------+
            ^
            | 1
            | 
            | *
+---------------------------+
|    RecommendedAction      |
+---------------------------+
| - actionType              |
